Package: libxapian-glib-1.0-0
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GObject/C bindings for the Xapian API
 Xapian-GLib is a wrapper library that offers a C API and GObject types
 for the Xapian database. Xapian-GLib allows accessing the Xapian API in
 various languages, through the GObject Introspection API.

Package: gir1.2-xapian-1.0
Section: universe/introspection
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${gir:Depends}
Description: GObject Introspection typelib for Xapian-GLib
 Xapian-GLib is a wrapper library that offers a C API and GObject types
 for the Xapian database. Xapian-GLib allows accessing the Xapian API in
 various languages, through the GObject Introspection API.
 .
 This package provides the Xapian-GLib GObject Introspection type
 library.

